<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink316">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>poṉcey pāṇṭiṟ polaṅkala nantat</l>
<l>tēraka lalku lavvari vāṭa</l>
<l>viṟantōr maṉṟa tāmē piṟaṅkumalaip</l>
<l>pullarai yōmai nīṭiya</l>
<l>pulivaḻaṅ katara kāṉat tāṉē</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
  <l>Alas! He traversed the forest with roads paths,</l>
  <l>where in the lofty mountains toothbrush trees with dark trunks grow long,</l>
  <l>and tigers roam about – to make fade the pretty outline of hips, </l>
  <l>that are wide as a chariot,</l>
  <l>and abound with round jewels, made of gold.</l>
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
